    "Similarly, P4 said: \"We are currently working a bit more on monitoring, not specifically for the environment yet.",
    "Still, we are now logging and monitoring, for example, how many tokens are used as input and output from these models.",
    "We could also use that to monitor environments, maybe emissions."
